sentences.sContent: ...some of the preeminent names in baseball.

remMethod.val: pre(在前面) + eminent(著名的) → 比著名的人还著名 → 出类拔萃的

trans.tranCn: 出类拔萃的， 杰出的
trans.tranOther: If someone or something is preeminent in a group, they are more important, powerful, or capable than other people or things in the group
